text: Stephen Tataw (31 March 1963 - 31 July 2020) was a Cameroonian football player. He played for Cameroon national team. Tataw died on 31 July 2020 in Yaoundé at the age of 57.Cameroon's Italia '90 captain Stephen Tataw dies ==Honours== ===Club=== *Cameroon Cup: 1989, 1991 and 1992 ===International=== *Africa Cup of Nations: 1988 ==References== Category:1963 births Category:2020 deaths Category:Cameroonian footballers Category:People from Yaoundé
